_sText:
This is my second map! A glass map :D Includes a funny sound every time there's a new round start! There's 2 secret places. In one of them you can put the song "Billy Talent - Fallen Leaves" on! And in the other place you put the lasers on :) I got inspired from another map named: glass_trap_final
One of my favorite maps :)

Map name: glass_cornix_beta2.bsp
Nap size: 12 245 kb :O Thanks to the music! But it's worth it ;)

*NOTE* THIS IS A BETA VERSION! THIS MEANS THAT THE MAP IS NOT FULLY DONE YET AND CAN HAVE SOME BUGS IN IT! PLEASE REPORT ALL BUGS TO THIS EMAIL: Johandahl11@hotmail.com , thanks! :D
